BƯỚC 2 — VIẾT TEST PLAN
- Objective: The objective of this test plan is to verify the functionality, performance, and data quality of the User API.
This includes validating API responses, mandatory fields, data types, and ensuring data integrity after extracting data into CSV or database.

- SCOPE (PHẠM VI TEST):
+ API Functional Testing for GET /users
+ Response status code validation
+ Response time validation
+ Mandatory field validation (id, name, email)
+ Data type validation
+ Data quality validation (NULL, duplicate, format)
+ Data consistency(tính nhất quán) between API and CSV/database

- TEST TYPES (LOẠI TEST):
+ Test Types
+ Functional Testing
+ Data Validation Testing
+ Basic Performance Testing (response time)

- TOOLS & TECHNOLOGIES:
+ Python (for test scripts)
+ Requests library (API testing)
+ Pandas (data validation)
+ CSV / SQLite / MySQL (data storage)
+ GitHub (version control)

- ENTRY CRITERIA (ĐIỀU KIỆN BẮT ĐẦU TEST): 
+ API endpoint is accessible
+ Test environment is ready
+ Test data is available
+ Test plan and test cases are approved

- EXIT CRITERIA (ĐIỀU KIỆN KẾT THÚC TEST):
+ All planned test cases are executed
+ No critical or high severity defects remain open
+ Test results are documented
+ Test execution summary is completed